body:
can we convert some of our submodules to cmake external project?
that would address the issue of always pulling source code for optional components (of which we have many)
git clone --recursive of onnxruntime repo takes forever because of all the nested submodules that were added the past few months. it also slows down CI pipelines.

start by making grpc a cmake external project. looks like there is a submodule in there that cannot be accessed behind GFC.
